{
  "stem": "598.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we stayed there in that-- in that yard till 5 o'clock in the afternoon. 5 o'clock he called up, he said, it was no-- nobody stood against him.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He says, you can go away, and you can live another four months.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You can go home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And from now on, it's going to be a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he tell us which streets were going to be a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He gave us three days to go from out-- wherever we have houses, over there, are going to be a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we had to [INAUDIBLE] from-- this was on Thursday, Friday-- Sunday was the first day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "From Sunday we had a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We had to stay in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "In that time was killed 2,500 people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We knew already, arrived 12 o'clock a day. 12 o'clock came, a full horse and wagon with clothing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And they took from us, the people-- the 120 men-- they took some of them to unload.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So they came in, they say, we  have just unloaded the clothing from the people that were killed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Because that's what we knew already, 12 o'clock that day, that they were killed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was worse.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know exactly what that's going to be.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Either in April or May.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'42. 1942.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was back-- I found out that when you work for Germans, then you're more sure than when you work for the sugar factory.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went to the Germans, and I worked for the Germans to break up stones.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father went to the sugar factory again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went to-- they gave me a job to drill holes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have to put ammunition there and take them apart.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was working there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, it was very hard and a dangerous job.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
